# Spotilyzer

Welcome to **Spotilyzer**, your comprehensive tool for analyzing and visualizing your Spotify listening habits. Connect your Spotify account to gain insights into your most-listened-to songs and artists, track your listening trends, and discover new music tailored to your tastes.

## üöÄ Key Features

- **Seamless Spotify Integration**: Easily connect and authenticate your Spotify account to access your listening data securely.
- **Comprehensive Analytics**: Rank your top songs and artists by total listening time, providing a clear overview of your musical preferences.
- **Personalized Recommendations**: Receive curated suggestions for new music based on your most-listened tracks and artists.
- **Intuitive Dashboard**: Explore your music statistics through a user-friendly and visually appealing interface.

## üõ†Ô∏è Technologies Used

- **Frontend**: React.js for a dynamic and responsive user interface.
- **Backend**: Node.js with Express.js to handle API requests and data processing.
- **Database**: MongoDB for efficient storage and retrieval of user and listening data.
- **Authentication**: Spotify OAuth for secure account linking and data access.
- **Deployment**: Hosted on [Your Preferred Hosting Service], ensuring reliability and scalability.

## üì• Getting Started

### **Prerequisites**

